{"tid":1505390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要贏，有兩條路。","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:37:26.000Z","uid":280341,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"d192e5ada55a87adb41e4c2eb23cf7ba25e797eb","tid":1505390,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"無論係真狗定警狗，習性都係一樣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你走佢就追，你追佢就走。</span></span></strong><br />\n運動至今，我地無所畏懼，但係警狗幾乎毫髮無損，更加無野驚，所以下下shot頭又點話？？運動已經去到樽頸位，大家受嘅傷太多，勇武已經去到臨界點，釋放翻D技能，應該好應該。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">黎到今日，我地應該都要諗諗咩叫「視死如歸」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.對恃嘅時候，分定30-50人一隊（一定要自己開group自己人），唔係諗邊條路線撤退，而係當哨兵通知警狗分隊包抄嘅時候，就要搵兩架以下嘅狗車攻擊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">插釱-&gt;毀車-&gt;打狗</span></strong></span>。只要唔死人，打得贏，就無襲警呢回事。 毀車好重要，一定要令對手驚，先有得打。<br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下次再入機場。唔係集會，而係佔領。</span></span></strong>佔中環佔旺角佔立法會，不能直接破壞經濟，不痛不癢。但係佔領機場，一日就過千萬損失。經濟所連帶嘅蝴蝶效應，絕對超乎想像，政府已經出曬絕招，又封鐵又清算咁，林鄭已被中共杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地都好應該送翻份大禮俾祖國，幫佢慶祝建黨70周年。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aaf085848f33952fb9ec9cb19acdfb4bbbb90e52","tid":1505390,"uid":259613,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:59:59.000Z","msg":"毀車好重要 係真<br />\n佢地出入全部用車"},{"pid":"c45c22332f0f4a2693e439bc4fb12df81121a29f","tid":1505390,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f96bf296c1f1b19f47868756ac2f1aec95b468e","tid":1505390,"uid":149653,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"大撚把左膠阻你插釱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1748b2287b2cc7c850694c82ff2ab8a86735158f","tid":1505390,"uid":149653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"大撚把左膠阻你毀車"},{"pid":"6dc4e536ac206609c9b8d6d3c0378ae946f594f9","tid":1505390,"uid":149653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"大撚把左膠阻你打狗"},{"pid":"6a5834e460099af25034e38bdb46ec8a9c6d7385","tid":1505390,"uid":149653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:03:47.000Z","msg":"要做要先無視左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d893d14ccdd6d888a6b33c0cf054fa5dadf1701e","tid":1505390,"uid":149653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"順手再幫你推多下"},{"pid":"c2e6d1067ef1841d33dd6a03b84d080e6264d99a","tid":1505390,"uid":149653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"雖然你係P牌 但你諗野正路"},{"pid":"6c3c8777f242db5701c28daf29ccb3d899314c3b","tid":1505390,"uid":280341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"今時今日，勇武打得贏 ，就可以幫和理非升埋級。"},{"pid":"d682af1bce4a4161a90a7471ce63b483876122a7","tid":1505390,"uid":270398,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"aaf085848f33952fb9ec9cb19acdfb4bbbb90e52","tid":1505390,"uid":259613,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:59:59.000Z","msg":"毀車好重要 係真<br />\n佢地出入全部用車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"係, 要完全破壞到架車用唔番, 車呢D野唔係話有錢就可以短時間內變出黎, 爆車變相可以降低佢地行動力同人數"},{"pid":"85ed47d52e3f84ef168d85897a54a167b3dbd73d","tid":1505390,"uid":282321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"880f15cf9faf487bfa468e441746c3e551c772a1","tid":1505390,"uid":59511,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:13:53.000Z","msg":"如果唔係有意武裝革命嘅，佔機場根本弱智。<br />\n班狗之所以有所忌憚係因為有外國遊客、有錢佬做人盾。你佔領完冇晒啲盾佢落晒閘放狗就一車車兄弟流住血同淚去新狗屋"},{"pid":"f4eb81aca8caa89f1748a17d1977627797b2d903","tid":1505390,"ui