583693291%2FO1CN01jPWPOM1aBJwz8mCSm_%21%21583693291.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=bcb8a5f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.alicdn.com/img/bao/uploaded/i4/i2/583693291/O1CN01jPWPOM1aBJwz8mCSm_!!583693291.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.alicdn.com/img/bao/uploaded/i4/i4/828822875/TB2.NTtgirpK1RjSZFhXXXSdXXa_!!828822875.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fbao%2Fuploaded%2Fi4%2Fi4%2F828822875%2FTB2.NTtgirpK1RjSZFhXXXSdXXa_%21%21828822875.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=6001dc18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.alicdn.com/img/bao/uploaded/i4/i4/828822875/TB2.NTtgirpK1RjSZFhXXXSdXXa_!!828822875.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"cd81cc19c9e9c8305a1df5713ff80e63c329ac22","tid":1505390,"uid":148824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"對敵人仁慈=對自己殘忍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dbd9acb3cf19526ae129c0374a4c8ed0e6b3daea","tid":1505390,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d192e5ada55a87adb41e4c2eb23cf7ba25e797eb","tid":1505390,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"無論係真狗定警狗，習性都係一樣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你走佢就追，你追佢就走。</span></span></strong><br />\n運動至今，我地無所畏懼，但係警狗幾乎毫髮無損，更加無野驚，所以下下shot頭又點話？？運動已經去到樽頸位，大家受嘅傷太多，勇武已經去到臨界點，釋放翻D技能，應該好應該。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">黎到今日，我地應該都要諗諗咩叫「視死如歸」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.對恃嘅時候，分定30-50人一隊（一定要自己開group自己人），唔係諗邊條路線撤退，而係當哨兵通知警狗分隊包抄嘅時候，就要搵兩架以下嘅狗車攻擊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">插釱-&gt;毀車-&gt;打狗</span></strong></span>。只要唔死人，打得贏，就無襲警呢回事。 毀車好重要，一定要令對手驚，先有得打。<br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下次再入機場。唔係集會，而係佔領。</span></span></strong>佔中環佔旺角佔立法會，不能直接破壞經濟，不痛不癢。但係佔領機場，一日就過千萬損失。經濟所連帶嘅蝴蝶效應，絕對超乎想像，政府已經出曬絕招，又封鐵又清算咁，林鄭已被中共杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地都好應該送翻份大禮俾祖國，幫佢慶祝建黨70周年。</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"但係一佔機場就會比人圍捕喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd3985fd129c630488491d91ecfea0c4e980114","tid":1505390,"uid":247305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"佢地冇性，已經同動物無異"},{"pid":"66e5b8f3c4d331924fb1a6220650ba5742474689","tid":1505390,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd9acb3cf19526ae129c0374a4c8ed0e6b3daea","tid":1505390,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d192e5ada55a87adb41e4c2eb23cf7ba25e797eb","tid":1505390,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"無論係真狗定警狗，習性都係一樣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你走佢就追，你追佢就走。</span></span></strong><br />\n運動至今，我地無所畏懼，但係警狗幾乎毫髮無損，更加無野驚，所以下下shot頭又點話？？運動已經去到樽頸位，大家受嘅傷太多，勇武已經去到臨界點，釋放翻D技能，應該好應該。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">黎到今日，我地應該都要諗諗咩叫「視死如歸」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.對恃嘅時候，分定30-50人一隊（一定要自己開group自己人），唔係諗邊條路線撤退，而係當哨兵通知警狗分隊包抄嘅時候，就要搵兩架以下嘅狗車攻擊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">插釱-&gt;毀車-&gt;打狗</span></strong></span>。只要唔死人，打得贏，就無襲警呢回事。 毀車好重要，一定要令對手驚，先有得打。<br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下次再入機場。唔係集會，而係佔領。</span></span></strong>佔中環佔旺角佔立法會，不能直接破壞經濟，不痛不癢。但係佔領機場，一日就過千萬損失。經濟所連帶嘅蝴蝶效應，絕對超乎想像，政府已經出曬絕招，又封鐵又清算咁，林鄭已被中共杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地都好應該送翻份大禮俾祖國，幫佢慶祝建黨70周年。</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2